import {Router, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'
import Footer from './components/Footer'
import Header from './components/Header'
import Home from './screens/Home'





function App(props) {
  return (
    <>
    <Router>
    <Header/>
    <Switch>
      <Route path= '/' exact={true} component={Home} />

     
    </Switch>
    <Footer/>
    </Router>
    </>
    )}

  export default App
